channel.title: Help me help you
channel.description:
I'm trying to get a list of every compile error that anyone has ever gotten. This is just about impossible, there probably being millions, but please take the time to post here telling me what compile error you have ever gotten.
I'm doing this because once I get a good amount together I'll post the list in tut section with their solutions.
This could help a lot of people so please help me get them together.
